# Presentations Project Rules

## Repo Structure

- `/docs/` — All company and product documentation
- `/nordic-global-solutions-hiring/` — Hiring presentation (landing + slides)
- `/rules/services/github/` — GitHub workflow rules (main → Netlify)
- `netlify.toml` — Netlify build config; publish directory: `nordic-global-solutions-hiring`
- `.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md` — PR template

## GitHub / Netlify

- **Repo**: github.com/zerwiz/nordicglobalpresentation
- **Branch**: `main` deploys to Netlify on push
- **Rules**: See `rules/services/github/rules.md`

## Conventions

- **Landing page**: `index.html` — hero, CTA, link to slides
- **Slides**: `slides.html` — full deck with nav
- **Content source**: `slides.md` — edit here when regenerating slides
- **Docs**: Update `docs/INDEX.md` and `docs/OVERVIEW.md` when adding new docs

## Nordic Global Solutions

- Platforms: Ona, WorkFlowSpace, Affiliate Flow, BitNexus
- Website: nordicglobalsolutions.com
- Design: Futuristic + luxurious — dark bg, cyan/gold accents, Syne + Outfit fonts

## When Adding Content

1. Add to `docs/` first, then to slides
2. Keep slide copy simple — no deep tech jargon
3. Match existing aesthetic (glassmorphism, gradients, gold accents)
